title: Now showing! Gorgeous 1003 Sq Ft 2 bed, 2 bath! Wonderful deal!
posting_body: ['Town Centre', '3475 Golfview Dr', 'Eagan, MN 55123', 'A wonderful home in Eagan is waiting for you!', 'We currently have a gorgeous 2 bedroom 2 bathroom renting for $1635 - $1755 per month.', 'This unit comes with 1003 sq ft.', 'We designed our apartment homes and floor plans with your comfort in mind, with beds ranging from one-bedroom, a larger two-bedroom, or a spacious three-bedroom apartment model.', 'The extra beds make great home offices, too.', 'Enjoy the view of Eagan from your balcony, relax in the community clubhouse, exercise in the fitness center, or swim in the pool.', 'Life in our community includes the comforts of a small town with the benefits of the city and the MN outdoors from your doorstep.', 'show contact info', 'Community Highlights:', '◾ Cardio Machines', '◾ Disposal Chutes', '◾ Elevator', '◾ Free Weights', '◾ Picnic Area', '◾ Pool', '◾ Recycling', '◾ Smoke-Free', '◾ Views', '◾ Walking Trails', '◾ 24 Hour Availability', '◾ Controlled Access Building', '◾ Intercom/Call Box', '◾ Laundry Facilities/Laundry Room', '◾ Off-Street Parking', '◾ Planned Social Activities', '◾ Reservable Clubhouse', '◾ Video Surveillance', '◾ Volleyball Court', '◾ Yoga Studio/Room', 'Unit Highlights:', '◾ Air Conditioning', '◾ Dining Room', '◾ Dishwasher', '◾ Intercom/Call Box', '◾ Linen Closet', '◾ Vaulted Ceiling', 'In Select Homes', '◾ Views', '◾ Walk-In Closets In Select Homes', '◾ Wheelchair Accessible (Rooms)', '◾ Wood Burning Fireplace', 'In Select Homes (3rd Floor Only)', 'Contact:', 'show contact info', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Leasing Options:', 'Variable', 'Pet Policy:', 'Dogs and Cats Allowed:', 'Max 2 allowed, One time Fee $250.00, Rent $30.00, Deposit $250.00.', 'Breed Restrictions Apply.', 'Management:', 'Weidner Apartment Homes, LLC', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', '7772AB8DCE774080']
